    How are ratings calculated?
    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.

    4.0 out of 5 stars Writing this review after 3 weeks of regular use
    Reviewed in India on 25 January 2023
    Style Name: i5/8GB/GTX 1650Pattern Name: LaptopVerified Purchase
    See if you were looking for a laptop that has good processor and a dedicated gpu but does not looks like a gaming laptop and gives premium looks and finish then this is the perfect option you are looking for.
    Pros :
    1. i5 12450h under 65k
    2. Keyboard and trackpad are amazing
    3. Has all the necessary ports
    4. Display is really great and 144hz is just awesome.
    5. Ram is upgradable to 16gb ( it has one 8gb and the other slot is empty so you just have to buy an 8gb ddr4 3200mhz ram and intall it)
    6. Read and write speeds are also good as it has a Gen 4 Nvme SSD. ( upgradable to 2TB)
    7. Games also run really smoothly as it has a dedicated gpu GTX 1650. I tried Valotant and GTA 5, both gives great fps and lag free performance.
    8. Charging is really fast as it comes with a 150 Watt fast charger.

    Cons :
    1. The screen wobbles which sometimes feels annoying.
    2. Fan noise is present when you are gaming which can be turned off but you will get low performance after turning off fan noise. But cooling is really nice.

    Note : If you are looking for good battery life in a gaming laptop it is very much impossible as 99% gaming laptops use H-series processors that consume power and does not give good battery backup.
    If you play games simply connect to the adapter and play any game you want.
    Doing normal task and buying it for college life, then you can get decent battery backup. No problem in that.

    No major cons apart from these two.
    You can go for it. It is worth buying and you will not regret after buying it.
